Provided by: scriptisto_2.2.0-2_amd64 

NAME
       scriptisto-cache-clean  -  Clean  the cache for a particular script. Removes the cache directory. Removes
       the Docker image/volume if they exist, but does not prune


SYNOPSIS
       scriptisto cache clean [-h|--help] <FILE>


DESCRIPTION
       Clean the cache for a particular script. Removes the cache directory. Removes the Docker image/volume  if
       they exist, but does not prune


OPTIONS
       -h, --help
              Print help information

       <FILE> A filename of the script file.

                                             scriptisto-cache-clean                    scriptisto-cache-clean(1)
